snippet.title: Video/DVD Review: The Dark Knight
snippet.description: Excellent sequel much darker, more violent than the first.

snippet.title: Movie Review:The Dark Knight
snippet.description: Not just your 'CRASH!' 'WHIZ' 'BANG!' comic book movie, The Dark Knight's nightmarish villain and the deaths of some major characters require a know-your-kid judgement call before you buy tickets.

snippet.title: DVD Review: Batman: Gotham Knight
snippet.description: Dark, bloody, animated flock of Bat-stories.

snippet.title: Video/DVD Review: Watchmen
snippet.description: Not a superhero movie; a dark, gory, complex morality tale.

snippet.title: Video/DVD Review: Rise: Blood Hunter
snippet.description: Torturous vampire bloodbath is a waste for all.

snippet.title: Video/DVD Review: Behind the Mask: The Rise of Leslie Vernon
snippet.description: Slasher film spoof has some clever twists.

snippet.title: Video/DVD Review: Alone in the Dark
snippet.description: Stupid horror movie based on an Atari game.

snippet.title: Video/DVD Review: The Brothers Grimm
snippet.description: Not a fairy tale. For teens and adults.

snippet.title: DVD Review: Batman: Under the Red Hood
snippet.description: Drug dealers and brutal beatings in animated Batman movie.
